description:
Варта пачуць першы радок, як успамінаеш той самы верш, які вучыў калісьці,
той самы дом, у якім збіралася сям'я,
той самы смак страў, прыгатаваных з любоўю самымі блізкімі,
тую асалоду, якую так лёгка адчуць.
Варта зрабіць глыток таго самага квасу, які памятаеш ты і які памятае цябе,
тое самае важнае, што ведаеш на памяць і адчуваеш усім сэрцам.
 
Квас «Хатнi» — высакаякасны беларускi хлебны квас 100% натуральнага браджэння, які прыйдзецца даспадобы ўсім членам сям'і.

«Хатнi» пiць — са смакам жыць!

title: Introduce WebCatalog - Turn Any Websites Into Real Desktop App
description:
WebCatalog (https://webcatalog.app) lets you turn any websites into real desktop apps and access to thousands of exclusive apps for Mac, PC and Linux computers. With real apps, you can work more productively and forget about switching tabs. 

---

Apps
Apps let you launch your favorite web services quickly in self-contained, distraction-free windows.

Let's forget about switching between annoying browser tabs! Unlike websites, desktop apps include many features to enhance your workflow: you can now set your favorite webmail app as default email client, switch between multiple accounts with ease, and protect your data from sneaky eyes with passwords or Touch ID.

---

Spaces
Spaces let you organize multiple web apps in a single place and switch between them easily.

Why? Because not all of us want to fill our computers with all kinds of apps. With spaces, you can now keep all your messaging apps or Google apps together. Or you can keep all your work apps in one place and personal apps in another, and celebrate work-life balance.
---

Privacy
Every app and account is isolated from each other, running in its own container - effectively protecting you from cross-site trackers.

Customizations
Customize everything to meet your needs, including ad & tracker blocking, dark theme colors, icons, and many many more.

Custom Apps
Turn any websites into apps magically.

Multiple Accounts & Services
Switch between multiple accounts, services, or projects easily.

Do Not Disturb
Control notifications with scheduling.


Learn more at https://webcatalog.app/

title: P1Harmony (피원하모니) – ‘JUMP’ MV
description:
P1Harmony (피원하모니) 6th Mini Album [HARMONY : ALL IN]
‘JUMP’ MV

[Apple Music] : https://music.apple.com/kr/album/jump/1690536589?i=1690536590
[Melon] : https://www.melon.com/album/detail.htm?albumId=11260282
[Spotify] : https://open.spotify.com/album/67nhgkEfNwdqQt7QFYHw0B

P1Harmony(피원하모니)는 ‘부조화(DISHARMONY)’ 3부작 시리즈부터 ‘조화(HARMONY)’ 시리즈까지 우리를 규정짓는 틀과 부조리함에 맞서며 더 나은 세상을 만들기 위해 쉼 없이 달려왔다. 여섯 번째 미니 앨범 ‘HARMONY : ALL IN’은 ‘HARMONY’ 시리즈의 마지막 여정으로, 필수불가결한 존재인 물을 통해 조화로운 세계를 완성하는 모습을 그려냈다. 

앨범명 ‘HARMONY : ALL IN’은 조화로운 세상을 위해 모든 것을 바치는 피원하모니의 의지를 담았다. 타이틀곡 ‘JUMP’는 힙합 베이스의 사운드로 진행되는 얼터너티브 팝 장르의 댄스곡이다. 고민하고 망설이기보다는 지금 이 감정을 즐기며 함께 더 높이 ‘JUMP’하며 올라가자는 피원하모니의 외침이 자유롭고 역동적인 퍼포먼스로 담겼다. 

타이틀곡 ‘JUMP’ 외에도 피아노 리프가 인상적인 힙합곡 ‘Love Me For Me’, 힙합 느낌의 신스 사운드와 808베이스 리프 구성이 매력적인 ‘New Classic’, 몽환적인 신스 사운드에 다채로운 보컬이 조화를 이루는 ‘More Than Words’, 팝 댄스곡 ‘Heartbeat Drum’, 슬로우 템포의 R&B 장르의 ‘I Am You’까지 총 여섯 곡이 수록되었다. 
 
‘HARMONY’ 시리즈의 마지막, 미니 6집으로 비로소 완벽한 세상을 완성한 피원하모니. 이번 앨범은 피원하모니 또한 물처럼 필수불가결한 그룹임을 깨닫게 해줄 완성도 높은 앨범이 될 것이다.

From the ‘DISHARMONY’ trilogy to the ‘HARMONY’ series, P1Harmony has been working tirelessly to create a better world by confronting frames and absurdities that define us. The 6th Mini Album, ‘HARMONY : ALL IN’ is the final page of the ‘HARMONY’ series, depicting the completion of the harmonious world through water, which is an indispensable element

The album title ‘HARMONY : ALL IN’ reflects P1Harmony’s spirit of dedicating everything to the harmonious world. The title song ‘JUMP’ is a dance music of alternative pop genre with hip-hop based sound. A free and dynamic performance captures P1Harmony’s message to “JUMP” higher together while enjoying the feelings at the moment rather than worrying and hesitating.

In addition to the title track, ‘JUMP’, a total of six tracks are included in this album: a hip-hop track with an impressive piano riff, ‘Love Me For Me,’ ‘New Classic’ featuring a hip-hop-like synth sound and 808 bass riff, ‘More Than Words,’ with a dreamy synth sound and colorful vocals, a pop dance song, ‘Heartbeat Drum,’ and ‘I Am You,’ a slow-tempo R&B song.
 
The last in the 'HARMONY' series, P1Harmony has completed the perfect world with the 6th Mini Album. This album will be a high quality album that will make you realize that P1Harmony is also an indispensable group like water.

title: Colgate pour les consommateurs de Café & de Thé!
Architect-Artist Innovates CG Film Production with CC AccuRIG, Redshift SSS and iClone
description:
https://www.reallusion.com/character-creator/auto-rig.html London-based architect Kay John Yim has set his sights on his next ambitious animation project, "Masquerade," following the completion of his previous works "Ballerina" and "Kagura." Yim is sparing no effort in creating this new debut short CG film and takes us through his character creation workflow in an in-depth video. He demonstrates how he streamlined the process by integrating the auto-rig features in Character Creator 4 (CC) and working with CC AccuRIG, Cinema 4D, and Redshift Random Walk SSS.

Yim's use of the cutting-edge Redshift software (version 3.4.06) paired with the streamlined CC-iClone character workflow synergistically optimizes the creation of stunning, realistic SSS (subsurface scattering) effects, minimizing the time required for rendering and lighting adjustments.

The mesmerizing vanishing effect of the star's cloak is created using Yim's advanced Cinema 4D setup, ultimately revealing her identity and opulent ball gown. His signature style of infusing each character with captivating charm and infusing glamorous sets with cinematic effects shines through in "Masquerade."

Additionally, Yim's utilization of the Edit Motion Layer feature, available exclusively in iCone 8, seamlessly blends motion data from Actocore and Xsens, resulting in his distinct and genuine animation style. In an age where text-to-image AI is ascending, Yim's work serves as a testament to human creativity, honoring the pursuit of art and provoking contemplation on its very essence.

"Masquerade" was featured in the 2023 Cinema 4D and Redshift showreel.
Access the article now for more Pro Tips and CGI resources from Kay John Yim. https://magazine.reallusion.com/2023/05/02/architect-artist-innovates-cg-film-production-with-cc-accurig-redshift-sss-and-iclone/

Kay John Yim works at Spink Partners, a British architectural design studio. His work in architectural projects span across the UK, Hong Kong, Saudi Arabia and Qatar, including property development and landscape design. His art pieces have been featured on Maxon, Artstation, CG Record and 80.LV.

description:
Merci d'avoir visité ma chaîne! 
J'espère que vous avez apprécié cette vidéo, abonnez-vous à ma chaîne pour voir toutes mes recettes. N'oubliez pas d'activer la petite cloche de notification en bas à droite de la vidéo, pour ne plus rater mes prochaines recettes 😊

Aujourd'hui, j'ai le plaisir de partager avec vous ma version du tajine de crevettes Pil pil, très facile et rapide à réaliser. J'espère que vous avez apprécié cette vidéo, si c'est le cas je vous invite à me le faire savoir en cliquant sur le bouton "j'aime" et abonnez-vous pour ne pas rater mes prochaines recettes. Bon appétit à tous !


La liste des ingrédients :

  - 600 g de crevettes décortiquées
  - 2 grosses tomates
  - 1 oignon rouge
  - 1 poivron rouge
  - 3 gousses d'ail
  - 1/2 bouquet de persil plat
  - 1/2 bouquet de coriandre
  - 2 citrons
  - 1/2 piment (facultatif)
  - 3 cuillères à soupe d'huile d'olive
  - 1 cuillère à café de sel
  - 1/2 cuillère à café de poivre
  - 2 cuillères à café de paprika fumé
  - 1/2 cuillère à café de curcuma
  - 1/4 cuillère à café de piment d'Espelette (facultatif)
  - 3g de gingembre frais

قائمة المكونات:

 - 600 جرام روبيان مقشر
 - 2 طماطم كبيرة
 - 1 بصلة حمراء
 - 1 فلفل أحمر
 - 3 فصوص ثوم

 - 3 جرام من الزنجبيل الطازج


The list of ingredients:

 - 600g peeled prawns
 - 2 large tomatoes
 - 1 red onion
 - 1 red pepper

 - 1/2 bunch of parsley

 - 1 teaspoon of salt
 - 1/2 teaspoon of pepper
 - 2 large spoons of smoked paprika
 - 1/2 teaspoon of turmeric
 - 1/4 teaspoon of Espelette pepper (optional)
 - 3g of fresh ginger

title: Mes tartelettes chocolat, framboises et coco
description:
Merci d'avoir visité ma chaîne! 
J'espère que vous avez apprécié cette vidéo, abonnez-vous à ma chaîne pour voir toutes mes recettes. N'oubliez pas d'activer la petite cloche de notification en bas à droite de la vidéo, pour ne plus rater mes prochaines recettes 😊

Je vous propose aujourd'hui des dessert tout en fraîcheur. Ce sont des tartelettes au chocolat, framboises et coco. Un mélange de saveurs qui va régaler vos papilles. J'espère que cette recette vous donnera envie de la tester chez vous et j'ai hâte d'avoir vos avis en commentaires ! bonne dégustation à vous et à bientôt pour une prochaine recette.


Les ingrédients pour la pâte au cacao : (pour 10 tartelettes)

• 270g de farine 
• 37g de poudre d'amande 
• 120g de sucre glace 
• 30g de cacao en poudre amer 
• 1 pincée de sel fin
• 150g de beurre doux 
• 3 jaunes d'oeuf (60g) 

Les ingrédients pour la couche de chocolat : 

• 45g de chocolat noir 
• 10g d'huile de noisettes ou autre huile végétale neutre 

Pour le confit de framboises : 

• 425g de framboises 
• 50g de cassonade 
• Le jus d'1 demi citron jaune 
• 3g de pectine 

Pour la crème : 

• 385g de crème liquide entière à 30% M.G.
• 100g de mascarpone 
• 75g de crème de coco 
• 50g de sucre glace 

Pour le montage : 

• 50g de framboises 
• 10g de copeaux de chocolat 


مكونات عجينة الكاكاو: (10 قطع تارت)

 • 270 غ من الدقيق
 • 37 غ من مسحوق اللوز
 • 120 جرام سكر بودرة
 • 30 غ من مسحوق الكاكاو المر
 • 1 رشة ملح ناعم
 • 150 جرام زبدة غير مملحة
 • 3 صفار بيض (60 جم)

 مكونات طبقة الشوكولاتة:

 • 45 جرام شوكولاتة داكنة
 • 10 غ من زيت البندق أو أي زيت نباتي محايد آخر

 لتحضير كونفيت التوت:

 • 425 جرام من توت العليق
 • 50 جرام سكر بني
 • عصير نصف ليمونة
 • 3 جرام من البكتين

 للقشدة:

 • 385 جرام من الكريم السائل الكامل 30٪ M.F.
 • 100 جرام مسكربون
 • 75 جرام كريمة جوز الهند
 • 50 جم سكر بودرة

 للتركيب:

 • 50 جرام من توت العليق
 • 10 جرام شوكولاتة مبشورة

Ingredients for the cocoa dough: (for 10 tartlets)

 • 270g of flour
 • 37g almond powder
 • 120g of icing sugar
 • 30g bitter cocoa powder
 • 1 pinch of salt 
 • 150g unsalted butter
 • 3 egg yolks (60g)

 Ingredients for the chocolate layer:

 • 45g dark chocolate
 • 10g hazelnut oil or other neutral vegetable oil

 For the raspberry confit:

 • 425g of raspberries
 • 50g brown sugar
 • The juice of half a lemon
 • 3g of pectin

 For the cream:

 • 385g of 30% M.F. whole liquid cream
 • 100g mascarpone
 • 75g coconut cream
 • 50g icing sugar

 For mounting :

 • 50g of raspberries
 • 10g of chocolate chips

title: Как нейросети помогают печатать быстрее?
description:
В рубрике «Вопрос со звёздочкой» разработчики Яндекса простым языком рассказывают о сложных технологиях.

Клавиатура — одно из главных приложений в смартфоне, которым мы пользуемся каждый день. В Яндексе усовершенствовали свайп — непрерывный ввод текста — с помощью нейросетей. Нейросвайп ускоряет набор и сокращает количество опечаток и грамматических ошибок на 30% в сравнении с предыдущей версией свайпа.

Менеджер продукта Александр Афанасьев, который в отделе обработки естественного языка развивает приложение Яндекс Клавиатура, рассказывает в новом «Вопросе со звёздочкой», как работает нейросвайп и что ждет Клавиатуру в будущем.

Aca Lukas - Zašto plačeš mila majko? | Pesma iz filma ,,Kafana na Balkanu'' (OFFICIAL VIDEO)
description:
Prodaja karata: https://tickets.rs/event/aca_lukas_4654

,,Zašto plačeš mila Majko’’ pesma je iz filma ,,Kafana na Balkanu’’ koja je rađena po životu najveće balkanske zvezde Aleksandra Vukasnovića - Ace Lukasa! Do premijere filma 3.11. u Štark Areni uživajte uz ,,Zašto plačeš mila majko’’ 

U suret događaju koji nije viđen na našim prostorima, a predstavlja amalgam nezabeleženo dobrog multimedijalnog projekta, svetske produkcije i fantastičnog sadržaja - premijera filma "Kafana na Balkanu", a potom koncert Ace Lukasa i Folk Haus Benda 3.11.2023. godine u Štark Areni, Hype produkcija vam predstavlja novu numeru najveće balkanske zvezde Ace Lukasa, "Zašto plačeš mila majko" koja je dostupna na Hype Jutjub kanalu.

Pesma je od prve do poslednje note satkana od čiste emocije, a zanimljiva je činjenica da je Aca Lukas pisao, komponovao i aranžirao ovu numeru, kao i još nekoliko novih numera koje ćete imati priliku da čujete u filmu "Kafana na Balkanu" koji nastaje po motivima života Ace Lukasa i demistifikuje sve detalje iz njegovog privatnog i profesionalnog segmenta života. Pesma "Zašto plačeš mila majko" prati životni put i prekretnicu glavnog protagoniste Peđe kojeg igra glumac Mladen Sovilj.

Saša Mirković, direktor i vlasnik Hype produkcije zajedno sa svojim timom prikazaće publici jedan potpuno novi koncept događaja, a sve što vi treba da uradite, jeste da se spremite za jedno filmično, emotivno i muzičko putovanje.

يمتد المستشفى على مساحة 14000 متر مربع ويضم أيضاً المركز الدولي لعلاج الأورام لفاس المتخصص في علاج السرطان.

title: Groupe Scolaire Atlas
description:
6 raisons d'intégrer le GSA :

1- Une excellente méthodologie qui a fait ses preuves (100% de réussite au bac avec 90% de mentions Bien et T. Bien)
2. Une école centrée sur l'enfant
3- Une équipe pédagogique accomplie
4- Des moyens pédagogiques de pointe
5- Une porte ouverte aux études supérieures
6- Un réseau des anciens florissant

Bienvenue au Groupe Scolaire Atlas (GSA), un institut d’enseignement privé inauguré en 1997.

Notre mission est d'aider les enfants à devenir des penseurs confiants et indépendants qui font preuve de connaissance de soi et du monde autour d'eux, de respect et d'empathie pour les autres.

Le GSA adopte un programme académique scientifique et technologique qui développe chez l'enfant les compétences pour faire face aux défis du 21e siècle, notamment :
- la capacité de questionnement
- la réflexion

description:
Maniti Expeditions Eco-Lodge & Tour Operator is based out of Iquitos, Peru and is locally owned and operated. We are an internationally recognized full-service Amazon Rainforest lodge & eco tour operator that specializes in Iquitos Amazon tours & Pacaya Samiria camping trips.

During our 20+ years of operation, we have worked with the local community by engaging in eco-friendly activities that help stimulate the local economy which allows us to responsibly place nature, fauna, and flora in the reach of travelers from around the world.

Our eco-lodge can accommodate groups of up to 60 travelers but we specialize in small group expeditions allowing a closer and more personal experience, allowing each traveler to enjoy the best of the Amazon Rainforest. Traveling alone? No problem, you will always have private accommodations but may share excursions with other groups but never more than 6 people on an excursion.

title: L'incredibile Pizzeria "10 Diego Vitagliano" e la sua Pizza Napoletana contemporanea - Sede di Roma
description:
🔔 Iscriviti al canale: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCrGwVyyxSR0AgnrvjXWcMRA
📍 Nome e indirizzo: 10 Diego Vitagliano Pizzeria, via Flaminia 521 (Corso Francia), Roma 🇮🇹
📖 Menu: https://123qui.it/vitaglianoroma/
🌍 Google Maps: https://goo.gl/maps/FuTGetR49dWt7MDMA?coh=178572&entry=tt
ℹ️ Informazioni:
Il grande pizzaiolo napoletano Diego Vitagliano dopo aver aperto la sua pizzeria a Napoli, a Pozzuoli e in Qatar ha da poco aperto anche a Roma in zona Nord (Corso Francia vicino Ponte Milvio). 
La sua famosa pizza è straordinaria, è leggera e altamente digeribile, morbida con un po’ di croccantezza, realizzata con un impasto indiretto con prefermento di tipo 1 bio, una lievitazione di 36 ore, alta idratazione e un bassissimo quantitativo di sale. Tutto ovviamente con materie prime di grande qualità.
I suoi pizzaioli al lavoro sembrano i meccanici della Scuderia Ferrari. Che squadra formidabile, uno spettacolo vederli all'opera! 
La bellissima pizzeria di Roma è una palazzina con 300 posti (150 interni e 150 esterni), 4 forni (1 dei quali dedicato al servizio gluten free!). Una grande attenzione quindi alla pizza senza glutine. 
Il numero 10 davanti al nome è in onore al grande amore per Maradona, suo ma soprattutto di suo padre che glielo ha trasmesso. È anche legato alla prima recensione della sua pizzeria di un giornale di Napoli che scrisse che quella di Diego Vitagliano era una pizza da 10. 
Davvero complimenti.

Cet hôtel de prestige est un véritable lieu de vie avec pas moins de 7 bars et restaurants, un spa de 2500 mètres carrés équipé de dix salles de soin ou encore une superbe piscine surplombant la ville de Tanger. Tout y est pour vous offrir une expérience de détente absolue. 🤩

title: Turns out... buying online courses can be a waste of your money!
description:
Turns out... buying online courses can be a waste of your money!

There are a lot of fake online courses out there, and it can be really frustrating when you spend your money on one, and it doesn't teach you what you expected. Maybe you've heard of the "Instagram Famous" people who rip people off by claiming to teach them how to make money with investments and entrepreneur books, or maybe you've been persuaded by a friend to take an online course that will make you a millionaire. But in the end, it's always a waste of your money.

🍗PUBG MOBILE: The original Battle Royale, the first and the best!
PUBG MOBILE is a Battle Royale mobile game created independently by Lightspeed & Quantum Studios of Tencent Games, officially licensed by PLAYERUNKNOWN'S BATTLEGROUNDS. It was released globally in March 2018. Built with Unreal Engine 4, PUBG MOBILE focuses on visual quality, maps, shooting experience, and other aspects, providing an all-around surreal Battle Royal experience to players. A hundred players will land on the battleground to begin an intense yet fun journey. Each player is required to scavenge survival supplies, as well as to exploit the maximum potential of the map terrain, vehicles, and items to become the last team standing on the battleground. Check your heartbeat and be on guard as the playzone begins to shrink. Multiple maps are available for players to choose from, ranging from Erangel, Miramar, Sanhok, Livik, and many more. Don't forget about the array of gameplay that awaits your exploration! Till today, the influence of PUBG MOBILE does not merely serve its purpose as a game, it is also a hub that connects players from all over the world and a brand that encourages players to live to their fullest.

title: Soundtoys SuperPlate: E. Plate III Style
description:
The EcoPlate III (c. 1982) was the third and smallest version of the EcoPlate series of reverbs designed by Jim Cunningham. All three plates in the EcoPlate series use a stainless steel alloy to create its reverberation and all three versions have an exceptionally bright and spacious sound. Soundtoys studied and added an EcoPlate III to our gear collection for the development of SuperPlate. E. Plate III is just one of the five plate styles and many features included in Soundtoys' SuperPlate reverb plug-in. 

Available now at www.soundtoys.com  

All reverbs on this track were created by SuperPlate's E. Plate III style.
Sound design by Laura Wolf – @laurawolfmusic • www.laurawolfmusic.com

title: Soundtoys SuperPlate: Audicon Style
description:
“The Plate” (c. 1971) also known as the “Lawson Plate” was designed by Gene Lawson (Lawson Microphones) in Nashville to be a more economical plate reverb for those who couldn’t afford an original EMT 140. It was manufactured by console manufacturer Auditronics out of Memphis, Tennessee. Soundtoys studied and added "The Plate" to our gear collection for the development of SuperPlate. Audicon is just one of the five plate styles and many features included in Soundtoys' SuperPlate reverb plug-in. 

Available now at www.soundtoys.com  

All reverbs on this track were created by SuperPlate's Audicon style.
Sound design by Hannah Tobias – www.hannah-tobias.com

title: TERRAKE FRANCE
description: Lorsqu’on parle de haute technologie, on en revient toujours à la  nature, ne serait-ce que d’un point de vue moléculaire. A plus forte  raison lorsqu’on parle de régénération cellulaire extraordinaire. Depuis  ses débuts dans l’univers intimiste des SPAs, TERRAKÉ a toujours été  fortement lié à l’univers sensoriel de la nature qui avait été divisée  en quatre éléments bien distincts : L’Eau, la Terre, la Lumière et le  Végétal. Avec le temps, la recherche TERRAKÉ fut approfondie afin de  proposer la quintessence de la nature au travers de la synergie de tous  ces éléments : une recherche scientifique de plus en plus méticuleuse a  permis de développer des découvertes de niveau biomoléculaire et de  repousser les limites technologiques liées à l’univers des soins.

title: ENCONA | Product Safety & Conformity Representative | Online Course
description:
About This Course
Every organisation within the automotive supply chain is obliged to ensure the safety and conformity of its products. To this end, in the respective countries and regions current legal statutes on product integrity must be observed, also the justifiable safety expectations of the general public must be fulfilled. With products conspicuously "unsafe" in the market, or whose conformity to legal requirements is questionable, those responsible are obliged to initiate the necessary actions.

In order to be aware of and to understand the many demands addressed to a product safety representative, comprehensive information and qualification is necessary. This is the aim of this two-day qualification: it is specifically geared to the requirements in the participants' daily work practice. The central topics of product integrity are explored, and the competence as product safety representative is developed in the scope of these five modules.

Target Audience
Automotive executives and personnel who are to be deployed as product safety representatives or who already hold that position.

Objectives
The focus is on the communication of expert knowledge that enables the participants to handle their everyday work more professionally and in a more targeted fashion as prospective or existing product safety representatives. The responsibilities in the whole supply chain from development through manufacture and use up to the end of intended use are dealt with.

After an introduction to the topic the organisation of product integrity, product integrity in the product life cycle, guidance for product nonconformities and examples for tools and methods are discussed.

Concept and Methods
During this training, technical lectures and exercises alternate in order to support the transfer of the topics into the participants' own work practice with a particular focus on exchanging experiences between participants and the trainer.

Prerequisites for Attendance
In order to attend this training, a technical and/ or business education is necessary as well as experience in automotive quality management, especially in complaints and recourse management. Furthermore, the participants should be qualified and experienced in the evaluation of technical product and process risks (e. g., FMEA facilitator, VDA 6.3 process auditor; designer/ developer) and be knowledgeable about the use of the organisation's products, the state of the art as well as the requirements from relevant laws and customer requirements.

Certificate of Qualification
After passing the test, the participants will receive a certificate of qualification.

Supplementary Material
VDA Volume Product Integrity and Conformity

View our upcoming courses here:
https://encona.org/course/product-safety-conformity-representative-pscr

description:
Skate, do acrobatics, kill, and look cute while doing it!

Have a look at the brand-new Gori: Cuddly Carnage trailer, a foul-mouthed third-person hack N slash action adventure.

John from Angry Demon Studios is your guide to all things Gori: Cuddly Carnage.

Meet a cute but deadly hero, who knows the best hoverboard tricks. Learn how to slay mutated unicorn army and disgusting bosses in style. Mix slashing, bashing, upgrading, and shooting to bring mayhem to your screen!
Expect fast-paced action, cuteness, gore, purring, chaos, dark humour, speed, violence, and creepiness!

Developed by Angry Demon Studio, Gori: Cuddle Carnage is available to Whiskerlist now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1299690/Gori_Cuddly_Carnage/

Come chat all things Gori, with the devs from Angry Demon Studios over on our Discord: https://wired.gg/GoriDiscord

Developed in Unreal Engine 5 and winner of the Epic MegaGrant, Gori: Cuddly Carnage is an ultra-violent third-person hack ‘n’ slash set in a futuristic neon world. A multi-layered and unprecedented adventure, Gori: Cuddly Carnage is jam-packed with vivid and immersive environments whilst allowing the player to perform gnarly acrobatics in a positively brutal combat experience filled with high-speed and intense destruction.

PUBG MOBILE is a Battle Royale mobile game created independently by Lightspeed & Quantum Studios of Tencent Games, officially licensed by PLAYERUNKNOWN'S BATTLEGROUNDS. It was released globally in March 2018. Built with Unreal Engine 4, PUBG MOBILE focuses on visual quality, maps, shooting experience, and other aspects, providing an all-around surreal Battle Royal experience to players. A hundred players will land on the battleground to begin an intense yet fun journey. Each player is required to scavenge survival supplies, as well as to exploit the maximum potential of the map terrain, vehicles, and items to become the last team standing on the battleground. Check your heartbeat and be on guard as the playzone begins to shrink. Multiple maps are available for players to choose from, ranging from Erangel, Miramar, Sanhok, Livik, and many more. Don't forget about the array of gameplay that awaits your exploration! Till today, the influence of PUBG MOBILE does not merely serve its purpose as a game, it is also a hub that connects players from all over the world and a brand that encourages players to live to their fullest.
